## mini-TS pour les events

add user test ; add group test1 ; add user test test1 ; mod user test -l ; mod group test1 -p ;
mod user test -L ; mod group test1 -P ; del user test test1 ; del group test1 --no-archive ; del user test --no-archive

sudo add user test ; sudo add group test1 ; sudo add user test test1 ; sudo mod group test1 -p ; sudo mod group test1 -P ; sudo del user test test1 ; sudo del group test1 --no-archive ; sudo del user test --no-archive


